{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc380a86b3","title":"南阳市市长关于对右派分子刘克珍的处分决定","origin":"赵宗礼《1956—1961：南阳反右志逸》未刊稿，2023年2月6日。赵宗礼，《南阳日报》社退休记者。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba6d98d56c","index":0,"year":1958,"month":5,"day":10,"articleId":"fc380a86b3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c1be023648","type":"title","text":"南阳市市长关于对右派分子刘克珍的处分决定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc380a86b3"},{"id":"3af1efd63c","type":"paragraph","text":"市第六小学校：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc380a86b3"},{"id":"924bceff07","type":"paragraph","text":"你校教员刘克珍在鸣放时说“共产党说理不走理”；在大学报搞“三比”和“三多”；“干部吃的白馍、玫瑰酒和鱼肉多，农民吃的红薯面馍、红薯干，红薯叶多”，“农民积极性不高是农业合作化造成的。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc380a86b3"},{"id":"90e3634957","type":"paragraph","text":"据此，刘克珍已成为右派分子，决定撤职察看，薪金由小教5级降为小教10级。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc380a86b3"},{"id":"edc04e95ab","type":"paragraph","text":" 市长  刘文祥1958年5月10日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc380a86b3"}],"page":{"id":"babd884be1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fc380a86b3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}